      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; ">
          <section class="" style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;一项新政策的推出，我们总先要考虑到，受益人群是谁，利好哪些阶层，从目前分析来看，个税抵房贷利主要影响着以下几类人群：</span></p>
          </section>
        </section>
      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <p style=" margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;  box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em; "></p>
        <section class="" style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; border-bottom-left-radius: 1.6em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1.6em; border: 2px solid rgb(196, 140, 39); padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;">
          <section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us">
            <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; ">
              <section class="" style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">
                <p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(143, 89, 2); box-sizing: border-box;">（1）地产商</span></strong></span></p>
                <p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
                <p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>从最初传出个税抵房贷的消息引发的地产股连续暴涨可看出，除了人民币加入SDR外，明显是受到房贷利息抵扣个税传言的影响。对于地产商，确实是一定的有利好，降息、减税等，都为购房者节约大量成本，从而推动房地产市场的活跃度,将会为去库存贡献很大的力量。对于楼市来说，是雪中送炭的政策。可是，市场总有其本身的运行规律，任何政策只会短期刺激，从长远趋势来说，影响并不大。</span></p>
                <p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                </p>
                <p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(143, 89, 2); box-sizing: border-box;">（2）中产、富人</span></strong></span></p>
                <p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
                <p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>收入越高节税越高，但前提是必须买房。提到节税，简直就是给中产、富人们眼前蒙了一层纱，不过如果看眼前也许真的让人以为是利好，别忘了还有房产税这个隐藏又随时可以会爆发的利空政策。</span></p>
                <p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
                <p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(143, 89, 2); box-sizing: border-box;">（3）普通老百姓</span></strong></span></p>
                <p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
                <p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>其实该政策对穷苦老百姓来说没多大用处，买不起房的还是买不起，买的起房的，还真看不上省出来的那几百块。按深圳目前平均月薪7000元的幅度来算，一个工薪阶层贷100万，20年，等额本息还款，共计要还的利息57万元，每月按揭6500元，其中平均月还利息2375元，那么在税前工资将扣除2375元的利息来讲税，这对普通工薪阶层来说，无疑是利好的。虽然一个月到手能多出1-200元，虽然这点钱在物价年年飞涨的今天来说，已经无足轻重，但有总比没有的好。</span></p>
              </section>
            </section>
          </section>
        </section>
        <p></p>
      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img src="<?php echo $filePath;?>fing30_3.jpg" style="display: block; margin:0 auto; max-width:500px;"/></section>
      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px;  box-sizing: border-box; ">
          <section class="" style="width: 6px; height: 6px; margin-left: -3px; margin-right: -3px; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(196, 140, 39);"></section>
          <section class="" style="border-bottom-color: rgb(196, 140, 39); border-left-color: rgb(196, 140, 39); padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 10px; width: 100%; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 0px 1px 1px; box-sizing: border-box;">
            <section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us">
              <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; ">
                <section class="" style="color: rgb(143, 89, 2); box-sizing: border-box;">
                  <p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">个税抵房贷会不会加大贫富差距？</strong></span></p>
                </section>
              </section>
            </section>
          </section>
          <section class="" style="width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right; margin-top: -3px; margin-right: -3px; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(196, 140, 39);"></section>
        </section>
      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; ">
          <section class="" style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>通过上面举的几个例子及分析来看，总体而言，个税抵房贷对中低收入群体而言，并没有太大的实际意义，每个月多出来的收入并不能给生活带来明显的改善，反而是对中高收入群体的收入有比较明显的改善。所以就会有人担心，个税抵房贷会加大贫富差距，能买得起房的人，享受抵扣个税的好处，而买不起房的人，却还要交比买得起房的人更多的个税。这个担心也不无道理，不过政府也指出：<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(143, 89, 2); box-sizing: border-box;">建立购租并举住房制度。</span></strong>这个政策会有一定的限制，不然会用税收补贴有钱人炒房。至于个税抵房贷，目前市场的主流观点有以下几种：</span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(143, 89, 2); box-sizing: border-box;">（1）对中低收入群体为主的首套房市场意义不大</span></strong></span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>个税抵房贷政策是在当前房地产去库存的大环境下提出的，势必也是奔着去库存而去的，但政策对中低收入群体而言并没有太大的实际意义，如果首先针对首套房实施，那么对中低收入群体为主的刚需用户刺激有限，也就不能有效提高去库存的进度。</span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(143, 89, 2); box-sizing: border-box;">（2）有效刺激高端人群为主的高端住宅市场</span></strong></span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>政策对城市中高收入群体的改善性购房需求会有一定刺激效果，高净值收入人群会通过购买力所能及的最高档房产来降低实缴个税，该政策的偏向性非常明显，越是高收入人群的缴税基数越大，税率也越高，如果高收入人群能够在选择房产的房价上下功夫，效果很明显。</span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(143, 89, 2); box-sizing: border-box;">（3）可能会推动房价持续走高</span></strong></span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>房地产市场两极分化严重，该政策的实施也许会刺激一部分一直持币观望的中高收入群体迅速决定购房，尤其是对北上广深一线城市而言，房价或许会有再一次的飞涨。房价飞涨的同时，也会刺激地产股，尤其是以高端物业为主的地产股持续走高。此前据媒体称，个税抵房贷最有先放开的可能是首套房，个人只有一套住房的房贷利息将用来抵扣个税。所以总体而言，这对一些刚需特别是买一套房的人来说，用处还是有的。</span></p>
          </section>
        </section>
      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img src="<?php echo $filePath;?>fing30_4.jpg" style="display: block; margin:0 auto; max-width:500px;"/></section>
      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px;  box-sizing: border-box; ">
          <section class="" style="width: 6px; height: 6px; margin-left: -3px; margin-right: -3px; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(196, 140, 39);"></section>
          <section class="" style="border-bottom-color: rgb(196, 140, 39); border-left-color: rgb(196, 140, 39); padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 10px; width: 100%; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 0px 1px 1px; box-sizing: border-box;">
            <section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us">
              <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; ">
                <section class="" style="color: rgb(143, 89, 2); box-sizing: border-box;">
                  <p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">个税改革现实中实施的一些难点</strong></span></p>
                </section>
              </section>
            </section>
          </section>
          <section class="" style="width: 6px; height: 6px; float: right; margin-top: -3px; margin-right: -3px; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(196, 140, 39);"></section>
        </section>
      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; ">
          <section class="" style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>众所周知，目前个税采用分类计征的方式由用人单位进行代扣代缴。除养老保险、失业保险、医疗保险和住房公积金在税前予以减除外，其他项目均未被列入税前减除项目。而在此之前个税改革的内容也仅停留在起征点的提高上。目前，我国个税的申报缴纳方式主要是企业代扣代缴。在这种申报缴纳方式下，企业财务人员根据员工的收入，按国家统一的扣除标准扣除后申报纳税。如果放开个人费用扣除、以家庭为纳税单位等条件，那就得彻底放开代扣代缴方式。</span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>如果放开代扣代缴方式，实行个人或家庭自行申报的话，以目前我国个人的纳税遵从度来讲，会有相当多的人不会主动申报。此外，如果个税改革中采取分类与综合相结合的征收方式，那么除了住房按揭利息可以抵扣之外，一些此前没有计入征收的项目如股息红利、房租收入等也要纳入计征范围，会引起很大争议。这样的话估计高净值的投资人不会再投资房地产了。</span></p>
          </section>
        </section>
      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img src="<?php echo $filePath;?>fing30_5.jpg" style="display: block; margin:0 auto; max-width:500px;"/></section>
      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px;  box-sizing: border-box; ">
          <section class="" style="width: 6px; height: 6px; margin-left: -3px; margin-right: -3px; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(196, 140, 39);"></section>
          <section class="" style="border-bottom-color: rgb(196, 140, 39); border-left-color: rgb(196, 140, 39); padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 10px; width: 100%; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 0px 1px 1px; box-sizing: border-box;">
            <section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us">
              <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; ">
                <section class="" style="color: rgb(143, 89, 2); box-sizing: border-box;">
                  <p style="clear: none; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">个税抵房贷不如降房价来的更实在</strong></span></p>
                </section>
